  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IBitmapTweenConfig
    Settings for IBitmapTweenRenderer.
    IBitmapTweenRenderer

    ICrossFadeConfig
    Settings for ICrossFadeRenderer.
    ICrossFadeRenderer
    Animated transition between two textures, where each pixel gradually changes from the start textures to the end textures.
    IImageModule

    IScreenshot
